--------------------------------------------------------------------
External data sources
--------------------------------------------------------------------

This product polls — but does not embed — the following external
data sources via their public APIs:

* GitHub Releases API
  https://docs.github.com/en/rest/releases
  Subject to GitHub Terms of Service. Optional GITHUB_TOKEN improves
  rate limits but is not required for read access.

* npm registry
  https://registry.npmjs.org
  Subject to npm Terms of Use. Read-only metadata access only.

Version data is written to Tencent Cloud COS (Cloud Object Storage)
under a path configured at runtime via `--cos-bucket-url` /
`--cos-folder`. COS credentials are passed through environment
variables and are never persisted in source.
